Package: remorse
Title: Translate Text to Morse to Sound
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Matt", "Dray", , "mwdray@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Converts a string input to Morse Code and back. Plays the Morse
    Code as audible dits and dahs (dots and dashes).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    sonify
Suggests: 
    covr,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
